text.tspan: Monthly surface temperature anomalies by year, Canada
The deviation of a specific month's average surface temperature from the 1991–2020 mean, in degrees Celsius.
Data source: Copernicus Climate Change Service (2024)
Note: The numbers 1 to 12 on the horizontal axis represent the months of the year, from 1 for January to 12 for December.
